    <h1>About Koicosmos</h1>
    <p>
      Koicosmos is a personal site for research notes, classical language learning, design thinking,
      and small digital tools. It is also a public profile meant to be discoverable by search engines.
    </p>
    <h2>Focus Areas</h2>
    <p>
      Classical languages, Latin reading interfaces, visual learning tools, writing systems,
      knowledge organization, and human-centered digital design.
    </p>
    <h2>Current Project</h2>
    <p>
      <a href="https://sensus.koicosmos.com">Sensus Classical Reader</a> is an interactive reading
      environment for ancient texts. It connects original passages with grammar, syntax, translation,
      historical context, and visual evidence cards.
    </p>
